  <div class="span8">
      <div id="currentResearchAndScholarlyInterestsContent" class="content-section">
        <h3>Current Research and Scholarly Interests</h3>
<hr>
<p>Synthesis, functionalization and applications of nanoparticle bioprobes for molecular cellular in vivo imaging in biology and biomedicine. Linear and nonlinear difference frequency mixing ultrasound imaging. Lithium metal-sulfur batteries, new approaches to electrochemical splitting of water. CO2 reduction, lithium extraction from salt water</p>
      </div>







  </div>
</div>
