  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>Synaptic proteins promote calcium-triggered fast transition from point contact to full fusion</span>
  <i>ELIFE</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Diao, J., Grob, P., Cipriano, D. J., Kyoung, M., Zhang, Y., Shah, S., Amie Nguyen, A., Padolina, M., Srivastava, A., Vrljic, M., Shah, A., Nogales, E., Chu, S., Brunger, A. T.</span>

