  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>Molecular mechanism of the synaptotagmin-SNARE interaction in Ca2+-triggered vesicle fusion</span>
  <i>NATURE STRUCTURAL &amp; MOLECULAR BIOLOGY</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Vrljic, M., Strop, P., Ernst, J. A., Sutton, R. B., Chu, S., Brunger, A. T.</span>

