  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>Resolving cadherin interactions and binding cooperativity at the single-molecule level</span>
  <i>PROCEEDINGS OF THE NATIONAL ACADEMY OF SCIENCES OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Zhang, Y., Sivasankar, S., Nelson, W. J., Chu, S.</span>

