    <li class="publication  article">
  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>Exploration of the transition state for tertiary structure formation between an RNA helix and a large structured RNA</span>
  <i>JOURNAL OF MOLECULAR BIOLOGY</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Bartley, L. E., Zhuang, X. W., Das, R., Chu, S., Herschlag, D.</span>

