  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>Mg2+-dependent conformational change of RNA studied by fluorescence correlation and FRET on immobilized single molecules</span>
  <i>PROCEEDINGS OF THE NATIONAL ACADEMY OF SCIENCES OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Kim, H. D., Nienhaus, G. U., Ha, T., Orr, J. W., Williamson, J. R., Chu, S.</span>

