    <li class="publication  article">
  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>A single-molecule study of RNA catalysis and folding</span>
  <i>SCIENCE</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Zhuang, X. W., Bartley, L. E., Babcock, H. P., Russell, R., Ha, T. J., Herschlag, D., Chu, S.</span>

