  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>Bioreactive self-assembled monolayers on hydrogen-passivated Si(111) as a new class of atomically flat substrates for biological scanning probe microscopy</span>
  <i>JOURNAL OF STRUCTURAL BIOLOGY</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Wagner, P., Nock, S., Spudich, J. A., VOLKMUTH, W. D., Chu, S., Cicero, R. L., Wade, C. P., Linford, M. R., Chidsey, C. E.</span>

