    <li class="publication  article">
  <cite><span class="title">
  <span>RAMAN COOLING OF ATOMS IN 2-DIMENSIONS AND 3-DIMENSIONS</span>
  <i>PHYSICAL REVIEW LETTERS</i>
</span>
<span class="authors">Davidson, N., Lee, H. J., Kasevich, M., Chu, S.</span>

<span class="details">
   <span class="year">1994</span>; <span class="volume">72 (20)</span><span class="pages">: 3158-3161</span>
</span></cite>
    <div class="detail">
      <p class="wos">
    <span>View details for <a href="/https://ws.isiknowledge.com/cps/openurl/service?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_id=info:ut/A1994NL60900007">Web of Science ID A1994NL60900007</a></span>
